<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="idb8959326-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2009—Subsec. (c)(3). <ref href="/us/pl/111/68">Pub. L. 111–68</ref> added par. (3).</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1989—Subsec. (c). <ref href="/us/pl/101/163">Pub. L. 101–163</ref> designated existing provisions as par. (1) and added par. (2).</p>
</note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="statutoryNotes" id="idb8959327-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea"><heading class="centered"><b>Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I78" topic="changeOfName" id="idb8959328-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea">
